Not by its hallucinations - because it generally isn't any. Not by poor grammar - because it isn't.&lt;p&gt;In fact, that's the problem. The text IS perfect. Having been trained on loads of written texts - including a gazillion books - AI written texts contains all hallmarks of good texts; Sentence structure, grammar, rethoric tweaks and what not.&lt;p&gt;What does that make of us who like writing?&lt;/p&gt;
